About Designer responsabilities:

Gather data from UX research, analyze the information to propose solutions entered on users. Be ready to build wireframes for validating ideas and design the layout on the next step. Have the knowledge to make a consistent prototype and test with users. Design animations and micro interactions. Know how to prepare assets and documents for developers. Understand about gamification to raise ideas for customer loyalty strategies.



What do you need to be a part of our team?

You need to understand the Mexican market and people behavior;


Ability to work from home;
Be an empathic person to propose innovative solutions for business problems;
User centered Design;
Know how to make an UX research and understand how to provide a better experience for users;
Build prototypes for testing;
Express your ideas on a wireframe;
Be a good communicator;
Have a good experience with the most up to date UX/UI design tools, like Adobe Creative Cloud apps, Figma, Sketch, etc;
Speak English - Fluent;
Speak Spanish - Fluent;
Have a nice portfolio to show your cases and experiences on UX designing;
Have experience with motion design and micro interactions;
Have experience with consumer applications.



What can make you stand out on this evaluation?

Senior professional;
Have good experience with gamification;
Actually have worked with games;
Any design related course;
Bachelor degree or higher;
UX certifications;
Be an agile methodology enthusiast;
Experience with 3D modelling;
Have a vast experience on the market working as an UX designer.



Come join our team!
